{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵在海上遭遇暴风雨，损失了二十包盐。随后被海沙帮追上并俘虏，帮主韩盖天得知他们知道杨公宝藏的秘密，决定带他们前往扬州。在船上，两人被关进铁笼，寇仲偷取了俏尼姑游秋凤的银簪。后来巨鲲帮来袭，海沙帮陷入混乱，两人趁机用银簪打开铁笼，用烙铁在船底烙洞逃脱。最终他们游向被斩断缆绳的偷盐船，准备逃离。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们至少没有了可逛窑子二十次的花费，老天爷真残忍。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "白老夫子不是常教人安于天命吗？我的仲少爷，一饮一啄均有前定，上天注定要我们少了这二十包盐，就不会留多半包给我们。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你说得不错，可能上天注定了我们是穷光蛋，连这剩下的五六十包私盐都要完蛋了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完了！我的海沙完了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "快走！迟恐不及。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "俏尼姑",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "现在才想到逃走，真的迟了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我'美人鱼'游秋凤若让你两个小子能成漏网之鱼，奴家以后都不再下水了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "报上名来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "我叫傅仲，他叫傅陵……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "还敢骗我。你们一个叫寇仲，一个叫徐子陵，都是宇文总管发下全国追缉令要擒拿归案的人。只要将你们送到扬州，交给尉迟总管，就可得到千两黄金的报酬。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_gui",
      "speaker_name": "尤贵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人为财死，鸟为食亡，若非这两个小子贪心偷了整条船的海沙，我们也不容易拿到这千两金子呢。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "原来我们竟那么值钱，自己把自己卖了不是已可发达吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "闭嘴！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "失之东隅，收之桑榆，今趟虽让东溟派避过大难，但却得到这两个值钱的小子，帮主亦有面目见宇文大人了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "告诉我！为何你两个乳臭未干的小子会那么值钱？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "帮主若肯不把我们交给宇文化及，我们定会把这个秘密告诉你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们看！这小子竟敢来和我们谈条件。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_zhi_gao",
      "speaker_name": "凌志高",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "听游妹子说这两个小子懂得水底换气之术，偏是武功差劲，此事非常奇怪，显然有点来头。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人来！先给我抽三鞭看看他们的内功如何深厚！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你两个的骨头倒硬朗，这些鞭子都经水浸制，普通人两、三鞭都受不起。看在这点上，假若你们肯从实招来，本帮主说不定会另有处置。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "我们值钱当然是有原因的，因为我们知道'杨公宝藏'的秘密。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让他们站起来，松绑！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们怎知'杨公宝藏'的所在？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "是娘告诉我们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们也知此事，是罗刹女把你们救走的，为何她不和你们在一起？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "娘被宇文化及害死了，所以我们怎都不会将宝藏所在告诉他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "帮主啊！看来这两位英俊的小兄弟并非胡言乱语，'漫天王'曾全力追踪高丽罗刹女，传是为了她典当的一块古玉，当时我们还大惑不解，现在该猜到这块玉必是来自'杨公宝藏'。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_gui",
      "speaker_name": "尤贵",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "现在这两位小兄弟来到这里，证明天命选的真主该是帮主了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "宝藏在那里？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "宝藏就在扬州城关帝庙附近某处，但必须以独门手法开启，否则永远都发现不了宝藏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那还不快点说出来，帮主定不会薄待你们的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "帮主若肯给我们十两黄金，那我们就助帮主找到藏宝吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "十两黄金小事一件，快说！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "听姐姐的话，快点说出来。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "大家都是在江湖行走的人，只要帮主把我们带到扬州城，立下不杀我们的毒誓。再送上金子，我们便大开宝库，否则我们死都不会说出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "宝藏内关密布，藏宝处深入地底二十多丈，除非帮主获得扬州总管批准，把方圆五里内的民居全拆掉，再把土地翻了过来，否则休想进入宝库。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "text": "就算我们讲漏半句，帮主都不会知道，何不大家做个好朋友，作个你情我愿的公平交易。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你两个小子不去做生意，真浪费了你们。好吧！我就带你们到扬州去。但千万不要骗我，那绝不会有好下场的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_gai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "韩盖天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人来！把他们关进刑室的铁笼去。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "馋嘴的小子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我看这韩帮主是个好汉子，我们还是和他乖乖合作为妙！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "希望回扬州不会给宇文化骨逮着就好了，唉！我们明知宝藏在那里，偏是没胆子去取。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你真能记清楚娘说过的启库方法吗？那太复杂了，幸好你的记性一向比我好。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我只记得清楚下半截，唉！当时娘在弥留之际，我哭得糊里糊涂的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "上半截可包在我身上，甚么左三右七，包不会出错，人家出了高价，我们自该交出好货去。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "睡吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们果然成了内功好手，早先给人打得皮开肉绽，现在却是皮光肉滑了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "会否仍有人在外面监视我们呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "假设有个人可以令你做皇帝，你自己又不用吃甚么苦，你会不会派人看紧他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若真到了扬州都不能脱身，那韩臭天岂非要把我们撕皮拆骨？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "先看看可否把锁打开，你看刑室里这么多工具利器，凭我们出神入化的内功，要钻个洞该不应太困难吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我也知道，但怎样方可不弄出声音来呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若我们把炉子点燃，烧红烙铁，说不定可无声无息在船底烙个小洞出来，那时就可趁海水涌进来时，以那用来锯人的锯子开个大洞逃出去了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "门外男人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有甚么动静？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "守门两人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那男人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来的是巨鲲帮的战船。不知那美人儿帮主是否吃了豹子胆，竟然敢来截击我们，帮主吩咐要到里面把那个小子看紧，绝不能疏忽，否则以帮规处置。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
